      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a masterclass in atmospheric induction. The S54 inline-six delivers linear power through its individual throttle bodies, with the dual-VANOS system operating perfectly within factory tolerances. The Getrag six-speed manual provides crisp, tactile gear selection, paired with a mechanical limited-slip differential for superior exit traction. Critical subframe reinforcement has been proactively completed, and the chassis remains free of any structural fatigue. Every bushing and damper retains its original compression and rebound characteristics. This is a concours-ready example with an immaculate undercarriage and factory-spec paint",
